===Languages===
As of Census 2000, figures for Jenner's zip code showed that of the primary languages spoken in Jenner 94% spoke English while 6% did not; of those, 2% spoke French, 2% spoke Spanish, 1% spoke German, 1% spoke [[Urdu language|Urdu]], and less than 1% spoke a Native American language.<ref name=mla>[http://www.mla.org/cgi-shl/docstudio/docs.pl?map_data_primary MLA Date Center] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080801065542/http://www.mla.org/cgi-shl/docstudio/docs.pl?map_data_primary |date=2008-08-01 }}, access date July 31, 2008</ref>

